bill.summary: 9/30/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on (3R-(3-alpha (R *), 4-beta))-4-(acetyloxy-3-(1-(((1,1-dimethyl ethyl) dimethylsilyl) oxy)ethyl)-2-azetidinone (also known as acetoxy azetidinone).
